<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text"><i>Pennisetum setaceum </i>and especially <i>P. ciliare </i>are adapted to fire and increase following burns, contributing to their spread. Both grasses establish better than native plants after a fire, and as stands age, they raise fuel loads (DiTomaso and Healy 2007, Lovich 2000).</div>
